Package: mapmaker
Title: Map Maker
Description:  The `mapmaker` package provides tools for creating and merging interactive maps. The package includes functions for preparing spatial data, creating interactive maps, and merging spatial objects with additional attribute data.
Video: https://youtu.be/tMYHrPMaOL8
Version: 1.0
